      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a wide-body 996.2 featuring the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six with VarioCam Plus. This example is paired with a G96 6-speed manual transaxle and the factory viscous clutch AWD system. The mechanical integrity is superlative, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal update. The chassis retains its original rigidity, supported by Bilstein dampers and four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers with cross-drilled rotors for precise thermal management. This is a collector-grade unit with flawless paint depth, a pristine undercarriage, and a strictly maintained service log, representing the pinnacle of the 996 generation's analog performance.",
